      "content": "# invoice model generates formal payment requests\n\n`powerhouse/invoice` (31 ops) is the second-largest model by operation count. Generates formal invoices from subscription and billing data.\n\n## Cross-Model References\n\n- SubscriptionInstance → Invoice (subscription charges become invoice line items)\n- References [[payment-terms model defines payment conditions and schedules]] for due dates and terms\n- May reference [[billing-statement model captures periodic billing summaries]] as source data\n- Feeds into [[account-transactions model tracks financial transaction records]] when payments are recorded\n\n## Position in Ecosystem\n\nReporting zone. High operation count (31) suggests complex line item management, tax handling, and status workflow.\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[ecosystem map]]\n- [[object relations]]",
